- paths: {{ source_root }}/middleware/auth.py
- contract: Every request to a protected `/api/v1/*` endpoint is authenticated
  by the auth middleware; authentication must not be bypassable via config, env
  var, or flag. Requires a deterministic code-layer implementation.
- evidence: pending — /sanyi init
{%- endif %}

